These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, may
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, western
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, pakistani
2 different games are played: monopoly, billiard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, lily
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
2. the mechanic is on the far right##1
3. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person playing monopoly is the pakistani##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
6. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Birthday      | may     | june       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | sudoku     |
| Job           | fisherman | mechanic   |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | superhero  |
| Nationality   | pakistani | indonesian |
| Game           | monopoly      | billiard     |
| Flower     | lily    | dahlia   |

