.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, teacher
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
There 2 different types of food: kale, mango
2 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, ritmeester
1. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the owner of the mouse is the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the person eating mango is on the far right##1
5. the person playing monopoly is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Game      | monopoly    | backgammon |
| Hobby         | drawing        | dancing  |
| Job           | police-officer | teacher  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Food   | kale     | mango   |
| Pet           | lizard         | mouse    |
| Cigar     | oliveros           | ritmeester      |

