There 2 different types of food: eggplant, strawberry
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, journalist
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, spy
2 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, daisy
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, skateboard
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the dancer is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| City      | colone          | miami       |
| Food          | strawberry   | eggplant   |
| Job           | journalist   | dancer     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | spy        |
| Game           | backgammon      | mah-jongg       |
| Flower         | orchid       | daisy |
| Transport     | bus          | skateboard |

