.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, hiking
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, nurse
There 2 different types of food: plum, banana
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, brown
2 different pets are kept: fish, rabbit
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, sailing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, electronic
1. the person who likes green is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person eating plum##1
3. the person who likes green is the person eating plum##1
4. the doctor is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Hobby         | card-games  | hiking    |
| Job           | nurse       | doctor    |
| Food   | plum | banana    |
| Color   | green   | brown |
| Pet           | rabbit      | fish      |
| Sport         | sailing     | rowing    |
| Music-Genre     | electronic        | techno     |

